"contain non-overlapping administrative units. The AOI must be smaller "
"than the raster inputs by at least the search radius to ensure correct "
"edge pixel calculation, as InVEST will buffer your AOI by the "
"`search_radius` to determine the processing area. Final outputs will be "
"clipped to this AOI."
